metadata.name: Picadogs #1
metadata.description: Created by Bone appetit 'Picadogs' is a collection of 5,555 unique 1/1 NFT pixel art generated by Team 'Bone appetit'. Each species of Picadogs is modeled after homeless dogs in real shelters. ‘Pica’ means to eat non-food items. With Picadogs, you can find a growing community that will help you digest all those negative feelings.Picadogs adopters can participate in exclusive events and receive various benefits.As you know, Picadogs are all rare but some are much rarer than others. Visit http://picadogsnft.com to learn more.
